    </p>
    <p>
      <fig product="editorEclipse authorEclipse">
        <title>Attributes View</title>
        <image href="../img/ec_author_attributes_panel.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>A drop-down list located in the upper part of the view allows you to select the current
      element or its ancestors.</p>
